/* Exception => Event he program flow ko distrub, terminate. 2/10
 *  c# object represent an error
 *  exception handle nhi kri to pro terminate,drowback * 
 3 thing happen =>
1) prog terminate
2) msg ugly show
3) statment after exception will not be executed 

Exception => abnormal event.divide by 0
is a problem that arises during the execution of program.

Exception Handling =>  problem handle krne ke liye.
sari classes namespace syetem Namspace se belong
jitni bhi c# me class he vo obj class se derived hui he.

ek property hoti he msg jo particular error batygi.

01 Index Out Of Range Exception => jab array ke sath kaam krte he.

02 Handling Null Refrences Exception => string null

03 Handling Format Exception => int data type le k string value dalna

* Exception Class And Its Use=> apni sari child class ka kaam kr skti.
* name pata nhi sb me ye use krege.

